========================================================================

Judge Yally's Arguments:

I see this issue as being similar to posting in a foreign language or a
strange regional dialect. In that, this is legal communication but if the
attachment does not appear for some players or a player isn't reasonably aware
of the attachment, then it is ambiguous. However, if all players receive the
attachment and the executor makes it clear that there is an attachment, then I
see no problems. I opine TRUE.

========================================================================

